| If things are working correctly, the calls to .bogus after throw and
| after aaa should *not* get executed.
|
| By changing throw to unthrow you can see what would have happened without
| the short-circuting effect of the exception.

: aaa  bogosity preserve  z" dizzying"  bogosity !  .bogus  z" a wee bit of trouble" throw  .bogus ;
: bbb  bogosity preserve  z" sheepish"  bogosity !  .bogus  aaa .bogus ;
: ccc  .bogus  catch bbb  .bogus ;
hex
ccc
